column4: Elon Musk-backed AI startup and Microsoft sign cloud agreement

column4: UPDATE 2-Electric-car startup Faraday Future halts work on Nevada factory
column5: DETROIT  Nov 15 Startup Faraday Future has stopped construction of a planned $1 billion electric vehicle factory in North Las Vegas  the company said on Tuesday  another sign of trouble for Chinese tech entrepreneur Jia Yueting  who hoped to displace Elon Musk's Tesla Motors Inc.

column4: US trade panel eyes Qualcomm patent complaint against Chinese firms
column5: WASHINGTON The U.S. International Trade Commission said on Tuesday it had voted to investigate whether some electronic mobile devices from Chinese companies contain hardware and software components that infringe upon patents owned by Qualcomm Inc .
